data.description: What a great location! Enjoy close access to the nearby parks and beautiful Hidden Lake or a quick 20 minute drive to get to either Denver or Boulder. This quiet neighborhood is waiting for you. !!BONUS- This home qualifies for the Community Reinvestment Act Loans and there are great incentives in lending! We have specific lenders to connect buyers with to take advantage!! Great main floor living, featuring an eat-in kitchen, cozy living area with a functional fireplace and two bright light bedrooms with 1 full bathroom. The lower level features a separate living space, an optional bedroom, a 3/4 bathroom, a media room including a drop down screen and stadium seating, an additional craft room, and laundry room. Imagine green grass in the HUGE backyard with so much potential and don't forget the solar panels! Invest just a little bit to make this home customized and reap the benefits of an immediate equity!!
